test_even_range:
assert [16, 18] == [18]
  
  At index 0 diff: 16 != 18
  Left contains one more item: 18
  
  Full diff:
    [
  +     16,
        18,
    ]
test_large_range:
assert [8, 9] == [9]
  
  At index 0 diff: 8 != 9
  Left contains one more item: 9
  
  Full diff:
    [
  +     8,
        9,
    ]
